      • getHelper

        public static ETSqliteOpenHelper getHelper(Context context)
        Get the helper, possibly constructing it if necessary. For each call to this method, there should be 1 and only 1 call to close().

      • close

        public void close()
        Close the database connections and clear any cached DAOs. For each call to getHelper(Context), there should be 1 and only 1 call to this method. If there were 3 calls to getHelper(Context) then on the 3rd call to this method, the helper and the underlying database connections will be closed.
        Overrides:
        close in class com.j256.ormlite.android.apptools.OrmLiteSqliteOpenHelper
